syntaxExplanation:
Here is the core syntax for TS Class Fields:

```typescript
// TypeScript implementation for TS Class Fields
interface TSClassFieldsPayload {
  id: number;
  title: string;
  status: 'active' | 'pending';
}

function processTSClassFields(item: TSClassFieldsPayload): string {
  return `[${item.id}] ${item.title}: ${item.status}`;
}

console.log(processTSClassFields({ id: 1, title: 'TS Class Fields', status: 'active' }));
```

